!! Here is the Root lexicon, pointing to all the parts of speech:

LEXICON Root    !!â‰ˆ  **@CODE@**


 AdjectiveRoot ;  !!â‰ˆ * @CODE@
 Adverb ;		  !!â‰ˆ * @CODE@
 Conjunction ;	  !!â‰ˆ * @CODE@
